OL,3,C#35,000 per year mobile speed camera
OL,4,Cto be introduced in Jersey
OL,6,FJersey's most senior police officer
OL,7,Fhas revealed plans to introduce a
OL,8,Fmobile speed camera to the island
OL,9,Fearly next year.
OL,11,FChief Officer Robin Smith wants the
OL,12,Fforce to lease a small, standalone
OL,13,Fmobile camera for #35,000 per year,
OL,14,Freaveled at a meeting on Wednesday 9
OL,15,FOctober.
OL,17,FIt could arrive in Jersey as early as
OL,18,FJanuary 2025.
