OL,3,C#35,000 per year mobile speed camera
OL,4,Cto be introduced in Jersey
OL,6,FThe mobile camera would be the first
OL,7,Fof its kind to be used in Jersey in
OL,8,Fthe past decade.
OL,10,FIt will provide accurate vehicle speed
OL,11,Freadings regardless of the time of
OL,12,Fday, and it is hoped this will reduce
OL,13,Fincidents of high-risk and anti-social
OL,14,Fnighttime speeding.
OL,16,FChief Officer Smith explains: "Our
OL,17,Fprimary goal is to enhance road safety
OL,18,Ffor all Islanders.
