OL,3,C#35,000 per year mobile speed camera
OL,4,Cto be introduced in Jersey
OL,6,F"By focusing on those who engage in
OL,7,Fdangerous and anti-social driving
OL,8,Fbehaviours which impact our community,
OL,9,Fwe aim to reduce accidents and protect
OL,10,Flives."
OL,12,FHe adds that the cost of the camera
OL,13,Fwould be justified if it prevented
OL,14,Fjust one serious crash.
OL,16,FA police spokesperson later clarified
OL,17,Fthat leasing the camera would save the
OL,18,FGovernment of Jersey from buying
OL,19,Fequipment that would quickly go out of
OL,20,Fdate.
